    "OpportunitiesDespite these challenges, deep learning-based fault localization techniques present the following promising opportunities.• Data augmentation.",
    "As discussed in current challenges, existing DLFL approaches are suffering from low-quality data that are imbalanced or of limited scale.",
    "Thus data augmentation methods offer avenues for addressing the challenge.• Enhancing multiple FL.",
    "Existing DLFL approaches generally assume that there is only one bug in the target project.",
    "However, a real-world buggy project often contains multiple bugs."
  ],
